org.elasticsearch.cluster.routing

Interface RoutingChangesObserver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IndexMetaDataUpdater, RoutingChangesObserver.AbstractRoutingChangesObserver, RoutingChangesObserver.DelegatingRoutingChangesObserver, RoutingNodesChangedObserver

    public interface RoutingChangesObserver
    Records changes made to RoutingNodes during an allocation round.
